Introduction

BLINGONE is a multinational girl group.

Their first sub-unit, BLINGONE-PE, debuted on June 27, 2024, with the digital single "Kiss & Call". The unit was formed through the “CLICK THE STAR - PERU” audition, where members competed with over 5,000 contestants in Peru to come to Korea and debut as a group.
